From Setup, enter Process Builder in the Quick Find box, select Process Builder, and then click New.
Name the process Closed Won Opportunities. The API name updates to Closed_Won_Opportunities when you tab out of the Name field.
For the description, enter If a high-value opportunity is closed and won, create a draft contract and a follow-up task for the account owner.
Configure the process to start when a record changes.
Click Save.

